headline: Demand Uptick Boosted Zebra Technologies Corporation’s (ZBRA) Performance
summary: Delaware Funds by Macquarie, an investment management company, released its “Delaware Ivy Core Equity Fund” Q3 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
